{
  "stem": "7873.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [SIGHS] I didn't ever mention it to nobody, to my friends, and never even to my wife.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandfather used to rent orchards to make a couple hundred dollars-- zlotys, their money.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one time, my grandfather and I were walking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was way out of town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We walked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one guy got ahold of my grandfather, took his cap away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He dragged him over to a cross.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He wanted him to kiss the cross.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, my grandfather would get killed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he wouldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He beat up my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was only a little kid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I jumped on the guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He just threw me back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I fell on the ground.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And finally-- that was going on for about an hour.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my father-- my grandfather wouldn't go away till he gives him back his cap.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And finally, I cried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He cried.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he gave it back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] This incident happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was more than that to happen to other people, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But that, I-- I, I saw that incident.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That happened to father-- my grandfather, rather.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Certain, certain Polish people were getting ready to invite Hitler.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were happy to invite to-- even though he came in, and he ruined the whole country.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But they weren't smart enough to realize that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yeah, we expected it because if you listened to a radio in, in German-- you could listen to the radio, hear Hitler's speeches, and everything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, of course, we lived 40 kilometers from Allenstein.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's a German-- already in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we could hear the hate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The speeches he's-- every speech was in-- much with hate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I understood every word he said in German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is hoch German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- because we had ethnic Germans live with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
